assets.description: This is a model of the Home Cave stage and dancefloor inside TheWaveVR. You can import this into Tilt Brush, or any 3D modelling program to use as a template and create your own concert venue and visuals. Then you can upload them to Google Poly and access them inside TheWave using the Wave Builder interface.

assets.description:
I pushed one of my character sketches a ways further, developing it into a larger scene which I've recently added to my VR Chat world. It fits quite nicely within my dark and abstract environment. 

My world should be live in VR Chat next week (PC Steam game). If you want to jump and climb on it, join the "Surreal Hazard" world within the game. You can find this Blocks model near the foot of the largest mountain.
